title: Top 101 Free Agents
itunes:title: Top 101 Free Agents
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal break down Gregg and Wess' annual article "Top 101 Free Agents" starting with the top four on the list (6:40). What is the difference between Earl Thomas and Le'Veon Bell (7:37) and who has the hottest body on the list? (21:04). The heroes discuss whether the talent level of players weighs higher than off field issues (26:34 and why Terrell Suggs would be good for New England (43:36).
